column2: Control the Soviet Union with full control over both your military forces and your production. AI will help you with research, diplomacy, intelligence and politics.

column2: Control the mighty Japanese fleet and its marines, as you conquer the pacific. The AI will help you with other fronts, and handle the other aspects of your country for you.
